#12600
Nearby: Find the Sorcerer's Apprentice~
   Somewhere nearby on the newbie island there is a sorcerer's apprentice in
distress! Find the apprentice and the elemental rift, and see if you can help.
Follow these steps:
- On the newbie island, type 'nearby' to see what's around you.
- If there's a lot, try 'nearby Elemental Escape' to find the adventure.
- If you still don't see Elemental Escape, try moving to another part of the
  newbie island and use nearby again.
- Once you get directions to Elemental Escape from nearby, find your way to
  its location. You can use 'nearby Elemental Escape' again along the way. You
  may have to go around mountains or other terrain to find it.
- Don't be afraid to 'sleep' to regenerate movement points faster on your way.
- Once you get to the Elemental Rift, type 'finish Nearby: Find the Sorcerer's
  Apprentice' -- or just 'finish all'.
~
   You have reached the Elemental Rift and found the sorcerer's apprentice and
things seem dire here... This is an adventure -- a small scripted area with
stuff to do. Type 'adventure' here at the Elemental Rift to see more
information about it and try 'start all' to check out the quests here.
~
