#12650
Grove: Tranquility of the Grove~
   This little orange fox looks up at you, with fire in its eyes. It explains
that it is the avatar of the Grove Spirit, and that the druids inside have
become corrupted by rage. The druids are preparing to invade your world through
the portal, and they must be stopped before someone gets hurt. The fox believes
someone with your natural power can save the druids without violence. You
receive a totem of tranquility. Explore the grove, find the four druid leads,
and 'chant tranquility' to pacify them. The leaders are the Druid of the
Badger, the Druid of the Crow, the Druid of the Turtle, and their leader, the
Archdruid.
~
   You have tranquilized the Grove and saved the druids! Hopefully they don't
get into this kind of trouble again... You receive some magical food, in
addition to the wooden nickels you already earned.
~
