that it is the avatar of the Grove Spirit, and that the druids inside have
become corrupted by rage. The fox seems distraught that the Archdruid might be
preparing to lead an invasion to spread the mystical forests of the Grove into
your world, and they must be stopped before the Grove begins to spread. If you
could sneak past the Archdruid's minions and assassinate the Grove's leaders,
your world might be saved without too much bloodshed. Track down and kill the
Druid of the Badger, the Druid of the Crow, the Druid of the Turtle, and their
leader, the Archdruid.
~
   The fox looks down, sad, but accepts that you did what you had to do. You
receive some magical food, in addition to the wooden nickels you already
earned.
~
